{"tid":1198621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月11號晚，無論你衝定唔衝都照出席先","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T12:28:57.000Z","uid":92859,"like":101,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0242ce6e8824239d78adb57009cb76a71a841312","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"我知有好多人有家室有負擔<br />\n唔係個個都敢衝最前線<br />\n<br />\n但只要夠多人係現場大家就會放膽好多<br />\n驚既最多咪去到地鐵站上天橋睇定啲先再決定<br />\n只要你到現場就算只係靜坐擋路都可以係一種支持<br />\n你記住自己最盡可以做到邊就得<br />\n到時有一萬人靜坐抗議塞住班警犬佢都告你唔入<br />\n<br />\n12號敢罷工既就罷工<br />\n唔敢罷工就射波<br />\n射波都唔敢最多咪朝早搭的士番工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通宵一晚就足夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個世界唔係個個都係英雄烈士<br />\n但烈士背後都需要有群眾既支持</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知我係個唔敢為香港犧牲既冇膽匪類<br />\n我只想盡量做到乜就做乜<br />\n<br />\n求下你地，就一晚咁多<br />\n今次再唔出黎以後就真係冇得再出"},{"pid":"52830356a6324cd209257a0e1b590624b78edf77","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ab40b346bf7a645311ea8b0cf735d81ce7153bf","tid":1198621,"uid":45536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"12號嚟唔到 11號晚點都去一去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52da27d60578d2c7f586dbad7b3501b5d7b712c5","tid":1198621,"uid":157470,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"噚日俾一百零二萬九千人賣咗<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"46d9ee5bd0081f5c38819f4ddf08c7c5defb8baf","tid":1198621,"uid":2383,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKvgcfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKvgcfF.png&h=5468647e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下呢班渣滓 推"},{"pid":"bffccd501dcb5ca389a16926813b3d3ab8b332df","tid":1198621,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"講得好好"},{"pid":"e839466001ab58dcdf4f651482ece466b535a60d","tid":1198621,"uid":45536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52da27d60578d2c7f586dbad7b3501b5d7b712c5","tid":1198621,"uid":157470,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"噚日俾一百零二萬九千人賣咗<br />\n不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"講真佢地本身就係和理非點都唔會衝<br />\n你一早講定係武力行動 你覺得會有一百萬人？"},{"pid":"6ccc00004d9e26c2b47cf4aab8e1c1ed45424d05","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"就算得一萬人靜坐一千人衝<br />\n點都好過就咁得一千人死衝爛衝"},{"pid":"4984ed46f6408194f85659d7ca41b35f00ade1f2","tid":1198621,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3472a2550137cd581726a286f226de1b2df24c19","tid":1198621,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"唔衝可以cover衝既人"},{"pid":"48d1af2d5d2298af0e55c163c888e84fd7455bb8","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3472a2550137cd581726a286f226de1b2df24c19","tid":1198621,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"唔衝可以cover衝既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"冇錯，群眾都有群眾既用處"},{"pid":"f82aae34776e48dc716649e898f68723967e2a4d","tid":1198621,"uid":28279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"警察會趁尾班車後無地鐵增援時清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6af3a08cbc663837af76138b8e1b3f38d39c780","tid":1198621,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"自問唔敢衝 但一定會出黎 人多先會安全！<br />\n我都好驚到時人少會收皮 但人人都咁諗就真係收皮"},{"pid":"a384e1f97c1f04b63ef8b756eaf00e3f3b13ea60","tid":1198621,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3472a2550137cd581726a286f226de1b2df24c19","tid":1198621,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"唔衝可以cover衝既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"其實只要多人喺現場，就算得小部份人衝，唔衝嘅塞住晒黑警條路同埋用鏡頭影住，佢哋都冇得亂打人<br />\n要互相合作 最緊要係出嚟先"},{"pid":"3fea079bb8d5a56e24c6c4ad1d83cd8a4ba425fd","tid":1198621,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"衝？ 衝去邊？ 衝鋒21呀？"},{"pid":"72e0c61dc5203014f11adc9e63288ff9f1f1a9d9","tid":1198621,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"樓上話唔衝cover衝嘅人<br />\n邏輯錯撚晒<br />\n衝咗出黎仲點cover呀？"},{"pid":"df6f6b7ff8b2569a03074fa8a70e0db9063015a9","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fea079bb8d5a56e24c6c4ad1d83cd8a4ba425fd","tid":1198621,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"衝？ 衝去邊？ 衝鋒21呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"唔該哂幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a261c116aa3c016f6f07b9306e8fb985cc5bcfd1","tid":1198621,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f6b7ff8b2569a03074fa8a70e0db9063015a9","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fea079bb8d5a56e24c6c4ad1d83cd8a4ba425fd","tid":1198621,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"衝？ 衝去邊？ 衝鋒21呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"唔該哂幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"與其衝 唔好比建制返工仲有用啦"},{"pid":"731fa06414055ba6bf1a416be5f0f6c514e2b833","tid":1198621,"uid":84511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"五年前我地輸咗第一次<br />\n今次再輸就會係最後一次<br />\n<br />\n不同心態嘅人自有不同崗位<br />\n想做嘢但唔敢勇武嘅人<br />\n亦有方法強逼其他人參與罷工行為<br />\n<br />\n11號晚12號朝早攜帶食油、花生油、機油、汽油橫過係干諾道中告士打道等等重要幹線嘅時候<br />\n一定要小心漏油 橫過之前一定要買埋三角警示牌<br />\n漏油前二三十米放定三角警示牌先<br />\n漏完留係現場根本毫無幫助 最好拿拿臨離開搵人幫手<br />\n<br />\n11號晚12號整日要係令全港攤瘓<br />\n處理漏油事故至少要花兩三個鐘頭 絕對比佔領道路一勞永逸<br />\n油+三角警示牌加埋最多兩舊水<br />\n我地唔洗自己出車咁蠢<br />\n無罷工無出力嘅人自然會因為漏油事故幫我地出力<br />\n而你漏完油就走  根本無人會睇到你影到你"},{"pid":"1dc57e67e890c63014b3f65edf7c088a2a471ae4","tid":1198621,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57e40747f1f52dc9ac3d9996a72bb6bd902f82ad","tid":1198621,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dcbabc5f3fa8d8564dcca27a400879510163e63","tid":1198621,"uid":256131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"尋晚出完黎既 明人頭有幾重要未"},{"pid":"440a04800b3be2486011b380b0a3b0d2865d4b24","tid":1198621,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"毒果仲大字宣傳緊錯誤信息<br />\n誤導人地6.12號先出<br />\n12號肯定大把人諗住放收工去<br />\n佢地朝早開會 到時二三讀通過左 放工先去有尻用?<br />\n11晚可以騎劫12號民陣"},{"pid":"29a7e81393b07d85558fe91c1e3a7d8688a6e241","tid":1198621,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"基本過欄技巧<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199189</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8ecbc9bd1bd387463a25a870331b0edffa3009","tid":1198621,"uid":58623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"69個陣又話係咪都出嚟先<br />\n之後又話太多老弱婦孺阻手阻腳所以日頭唔衝<br />\n而家又叫人衝定唔衝照出席<br />\n咁其實611係預咗唔衝定預咗有人阻住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}